{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8973e91c-83ea-4c67-a9c5-5d9a571a4a6e","content":"No files found in the workspace. Since there's no existing file to modify, here's exactly how to convert your page to compiled bindings:\n\n## Add `x:DataType` to your ContentPage\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is the `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` attribute. This tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, so all `{Binding ...}` expressions are resolved **at compile time**.\n\n## Catching binding errors at build time\n\n1. **Misspelled or missing properties** (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`) will produce a **build error** automatically once `x:DataType` is set.\n\n2. **Enable warnings-as-errors** for extra strictness in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>\n     <!-- Or target only binding warnings: -->\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045;XC0022</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n3. **Opt out locally** if needed (e.g., inside a `DataTemplate` with a different type):\n   ```xml\n   <Label Text=\"{Binding Source={x:Reference myControl}, Path=Width, x:DataType=x:Null}\" />\n   ```\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, any typo or type mismatch in a binding path becomes a compiler error rather than a silent runtime failure.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d469703a-95d6-4456-bc8b-21e7eac75c09","outputTokens":518,"requestId":"A84D:2AD648:653BEA:74CDD4:69FBE1D4"},"id":"1c3279fb-9e35-4225-8184-62fda4ab193a","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:50:39.665Z","parentId":"2c031df4-cc22-49d5-9b6f-862f5fb9f540"}
